OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780495874
OL,3,CDriver with 45 penalty points snared
OL,4,Cby police in Leicestershire
OL,6,FA driver with 45 penalty points was
OL,7,Famong those captured by Leicestershire
OL,8,FPolice over the past year.
OL,10,FOperation Hopper was launched to
OL,11,Ftarget uninsured drivers and
OL,12,Fpersistent traffic offenders across
OL,13,FLeicester, Leicestershire and Rutland.
OL,15,FDuring the past 12 months, police have
OL,16,Fseized 105 vehicles, all of which were
OL,17,Funinsured and collectively linked to
OL,18,Fmore than 500 outstanding speeding or
OL,19,Fred-light offences.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
