PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780495874
OL,3,CDriver with 45 penalty points snared
OL,4,Cby police in Leicestershire
OL,6,FThe force said the 45-point driver,
OL,7,Fwho had a medically revoked licence,
OL,8,Fhad no legal right to be on the roads
OL,9,Fat all, with penalty points continuing
OL,10,Fto be added with each new offence.
OL,12,FMatthew Chester, road safety unit
OL,13,Fmanager at Leicestershire Police,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Operation Hopper intends to
OL,15,Fsend out a clear warning to those
OL,16,Fdrivers who think they can flout the
OL,17,Flaw and pose the highest risk to
OL,18,Finnocent road users.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780495874
OL,3,CDriver with 45 penalty points snared
OL,4,Cby police in Leicestershire
OL,6,F"Arrests have been made, cars have
OL,7,Fbeen seized, and we will continue to
OL,8,Ftake decisive action to protect the
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,F"This anniversary marks not just a
OL,12,Fyear of enforcement, but a year of
OL,13,Fpartnership, prevention, and progress.
OL,15,F"Operation Hopper will continue to
OL,16,Fevolve as we work to make the roads
OL,17,Facross Leicester, Leicestershire and
OL,18,FRutland safer for everyone."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
