CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780495874
OL,3,CDriver with 45 penalty points snared
OL,4,Cby police in Leicestershire
OL,6,FVehicles seized under the operation
OL,7,Fhave been scrapped, sold at auction or
OL,8,Freturned to finance companies,
OL,9,Fdepending on their legal status and
OL,10,Fownership.
OL,12,FPolice said intelligence sharing
OL,13,Fbetween the Road Safety Unit and the
OL,14,FRoads Policing Unit has strengthened
OL,15,Fthe force's ability to identify high-
OL,16,Frisk drivers quickly and effectively.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
